        Text View Constructor
        This sets the format to print to the information to a file.
        Parameters:
        steps - how many steps to run for
        p - the p value, probabilty of SmallCars and Motorbikes arriving
        q - the q value, probabilty of FamilySedans arriving
        pumps - the number of pumps there are
        tills - the number of tills there are
        gallonPrice - the price of fuel in pence/gallon
        trucks - whether trucks should be simulated
